name: The International Conference on Engineering and Applied Sciences
content: 2016 The International Conference on Engineering and Applied Sciences (TICEAS 2016) is scheduled to take place in Singapore from February 18-20, 2016\. TICEAS aims to provide a communication platform for academics, researchers, graduates and industry professionals to not only present their recent and latest researches but also share their thoughts and discuss the future development in the field of engineering and applied sciences. For more information, please visit: http://ticeas.org/index.asp or email the Conference Secretariat: ticeas@ticeas.org
